column1: EVTDESC_DYN;Choose a name for your new dynasty! There are eight pages to select a dynasty from.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;
EVTDESC_DYN.11;The Imperial Court has seen fit to grant you the rank of Marquis. This makes you a member of the nobility!;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;
EVTDESC_DYN.12;The Imperial Court has granted you the rank of Duke. This is a great honor.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;
EVTDESC_DYN.13;The Imperial Court has made you a King. Your power and prestige have earned their respect
